    • checkImminentAppointments

      public static int checkImminentAppointments()
      Checks for and counts all appointments whose start time occurs within the next 15 minutes of user's login. In addition, any appointments counted will also be added to the 'imminentAppointments' ObservableList.
      Returns:
      Returns an integer value corresponding to the count of appointments beginning within 15 minutes of user's login.

    • getImminentAppts

      public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<Appointment> getImminentAppts()
      Gets the list of all appointments occuring within 15 minutes of user's login.
      Returns:
      Returns an ObservableList of Appointment type, reflecting all appointments occuring within 15 minutes of user's login.

    • validateBusinessHours

      public static boolean validateBusinessHours​(Appointment appt)
      Checks whether an added or modified appointment's timeframe conflicts with office hours in EST.
      Parameters:
      appt - An appointment object instantiated from either the AddAppointments_Controller or ModifyAppointments_Controller.
      Returns:
      Returns true if an added or modified appointment's timeframe does not occur outside of 8am to 10pm EST; else returns false.

    • validateApptOverlap

      public static boolean validateApptOverlap​(Appointment appt)
      Checks whether an added or modified appointment's timeframe conflicts with an appointment also belonging to either the contact or customer.
      Parameters:
      appt - An appointment object instantiated from either the AddAppointments_Controller or ModifyAppointments_Controller.
      Returns:
      Returns true if an added or modified appointment's timeframe conflicts with a pre-existing appointment for the same contact or customer.
